{"tid":2293482,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"反黑組酒吧查牌 激動男：我同你講sorry Sir呀！","createTime":"2020-11-20T09:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T15:00:07.000Z","uid":54800,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b9e4693c71b35525fa367a13a7e80b7939e9aab4","tid":2293482,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"忠_ _ 毅 方上周六在中環一間酒吧查牌期間，多名<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>黑漢</strong></span>情緒激動險釀衝突，最後5名男子涉嫌行為不檢及阻差辦公被捕。<br />\n<br />\n上周六（14日）忠_ _ 毅 方因應限聚令突擊搜查中區一帶的夜店，其間接報德己立街30至36號加州大廈地庫一間酒吧，有人因碰撞及「爭女」問題爭執。大批忠_ _ 毅 員到場調查，。。。。。，情緒激動，不停喧嘩指罵，忠_ _ 毅 員作出口頭警告不果，最後以醉酒行為不檢及妨礙公職人員執行職務拘捕5人（32至40歲）。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，5人均有<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>黑幫</strong></span>背景，。。。當時有5人站在台階上與便衣忠_ _ 毅 員對峙，其中一名男子情緒最為激動，多次手指一名中年探員，喝叫：「我全程冇同你講過粗口呀阿Sir，我同你講sorry Sir呀！」似乎不堪「被屈」辱忠_ _ 毅 ，反指被對方爆粗辱罵，說：「你係咁x我呀...冇侮辱過你呀阿Sir。」又舉起手機拍攝。擾攘近10分鐘，。。。。。。，各人隨即鼓譟起來。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201120/KZOIW3NEJRGRHFFAZHHVBAXRNE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201120%2FKZOIW3NEJRGRHFFAZHHVBAXRNE%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=688bcbae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201120%2FKZOIW3NEJRGRHFFAZHHVBAXRNE%2F&h=872f6ca0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201120/KZOIW3NEJRGRHFFAZHHVBAXRNE/</a>"},{"pid":"626094ea67f603795bf7f8bc0523d281d8e16ff9","tid":2293482,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8697c6a107a5ac66e4206572631be335a2efbd4e","tid":2293482,"uid":352873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BrwOXpr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=